endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:1);
elseif(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_torch:4);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_torch:3);
endif;

UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!);

if(DIRECTION == "W"); echo(//set redstone_torch:4);
elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:3);
elseif(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_torch:1);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_torch:2);
endif; 
// wait at end of if
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!);

endif;

endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:4);

endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:4);
elseif(DIRECTION == "N"); echo(//set redstone_torch:2);
elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_torch:1);
endif;
// wait at end of if
UNSET(@done); log(waiting for done); DO; WAIT(20ms); UNTIL(@done); log(Done!);

echo(//set wool:4);

elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_torch:2);
endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:4);

endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:1);

elseif(DIRECTION == "S"); echo(//set redstone_torch:3);
endif;

elseif(DIRECTION == "E"); echo(//set redstone_torch:1);

endif;
